{"tid":1907163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衞生防護中心呼籲市民感不適應分開幾間房瞓","createTime":"2020-03-02T12:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T08:02:25.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"11d7348385d2906e501f165f88b09c3e62d3f8ba","tid":1907163,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君呼籲市民，若身體不適，應盡量在家中戴口罩，與家人分開用膳，甚至分房瞓；若年長多病非同居的父母不適，也盡量不要親身前住探望，應以視像或電話慰問，減低播毒風險。對於馬會投注站外大排長龍，她提醒市民「有病就盡量自己匿埋或睇醫生，唔好周圍去見其他人嘞；例如馬會呢啲地方，梗係盡量避免、盡量唔好去啦」，並失笑道：「如果去嘅話就要戴口罩啦&hellip;&hellip;一逼嘅地方，好難避免會摸到其他嘢；你去完投注，就一定要洗手㗎嘞。」"},{"pid":"89261ebfc2a4cb2de1857d65d7f2894b889c2ef1","tid":1907163,"uid":511,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"撚有咁多間房呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406c2350e524843811677ad46a2d01018b4a3bf8","tid":1907163,"uid":3502,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:08:36.000Z","msg":"一唔舒服就有幾間房比我分開訓咁撚有貨既話 我直接去私家睇完留院訓私人房唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb22940606740b8a29d1d778d37787d6447b81c7","tid":1907163,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89261ebfc2a4cb2de1857d65d7f2894b889c2ef1","tid":1907163,"uid":511,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"撚有咁多間房呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"買四房單位"},{"pid":"e22f96aca3104c19dd933bb8a1abdc9fb28368d4","tid":1907163,"uid":511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cb22940606740b8a29d1d778d37787d6447b81c7","tid":1907163,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"89261ebfc2a4cb2de1857d65d7f2894b889c2ef1","tid":1907163,"uid":511,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T12:08:25.000Z","msg":"撚有咁多間房呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"